{"tid":1872401,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你仲記唔記得自己對上一次開心係幾時？","createTime":"2020-02-10T05:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T05:50:18.000Z","uid":19194,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0d638adb0ed8f42b8f587f33c9c1aa8103bbae37","tid":1872401,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"最近太多事發生，自己呢排都好負<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以整咗個網整咗個專俾人放負、抒發下負面情緒既平台￼，大家圍爐取下暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OWdiOz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OWdiOz&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=f20ada5f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OWdiOz</a><br />\n<br />\n有時唔開心，￼打開個WhatsApp，都唔知道自己可以搵邊個講￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知應該點樣開口表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，￼￼好驚人哋唔明白自己￼￼￼，￼驚俾人批判，￼好驚帶到麻煩俾人￼￼。<br />\n或者之前試過同身邊人講完之後，不被理解，可能仲講啲好難聽既說話，令你反而仲唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n對於情感既宣洩，有時侯，會被視為一種懦弱。<br />\n<br />\n種種原因最後令到人唔開心就習慣自己收收埋埋，不過屈得耐，都會頂唔順..... <br />\n好多時抑壓得太耐就會因為一啲好少嘅事而情緒失控￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n每個人，都會有承受唔著既一日。<br />\n你仲記唔記得自己上一次唔開心同人講係幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n￼<br />\n可能，你一直以黎己經好辛苦、好攰、￼好大壓力。￼<br />\n￼可能，你一直以黎都冇好好正視過自己嘅情緒。<br />\n可能，你一直都忙於身邊嘅事，￼冇關心真正過自己￼。<br />\n<br />\n或者依加既你唔想講，但我地一直都會喺度，聽你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"ac0287949fc09818fe861239ee220a73217e5f81","tid":1872401,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811232e9aa295ff1afac14800213394b5eca2b9e","tid":1872401,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330745daab371f2dd2e6e16eb68cb08bf2d6a65e","tid":1872401,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"尋晚然波，執左幾千"},{"pid":"22d82c1b06768ec0d56a6333884ec23be18d722b","tid":1872401,"uid":335327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:54:15.000Z","msg":"琴日"},{"pid":"85a803faa495f52500672b4fdb8c70268f580c7e","tid":1872401,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"去旅行嗰陣"},{"pid":"856523039bfed40afd914551bf74f166edb65f94","tid":1872401,"uid":19194,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85a803faa495f52500672b4fdb8c70268f580c7e","tid":1872401,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"去旅行嗰陣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:33:05.000Z","msg":"不過返到黎香港就好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a575da8cfe657244c178b4207aeaff1026ed6e","tid":1872401,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"330745daab371f2dd2e6e16eb68cb08bf2d6a65e","tid":1872401,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"尋晚然波，執左幾千"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7177fe462ab19d0ead512e06b67d4be2a9c7526f","tid":1872401,"uid":42982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381da0e03a2ffafdf3ffc10e6184f66a58995103","tid":1872401,"uid":327401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"藍絲中肺炎死<br />\n果日開香檳慶祝"},